t": "如何看待 2023 年 8 月 28 日 A 股市场？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "欢迎大家踊跃发言"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-47f919e64dcfc7de3d65616585955031_720w.webp?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "85 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/619466329"}}, "attached_info": "ClUI+fCcl5nPzfhQEAMaCDk5OTM5Mjg3IPrmr6cGMAA42Q5ACnIJNjE5NDY2MzI5eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQDyARMIARIPZG9tYWluX29wZXJhdG9y"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "11_1693224875.139019", "card_id": "Q_618569270", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 697}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "一次去男朋友家吃饭，他妈妈在饭桌上说，「我儿子就是太老实我总怕他被小姑娘骗」，要怎么回复呢？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-e0db5f809a4011b75b8866dcde0eb9a1_1440w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "80 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/618569270"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I+fCcl5nPzfhQEAMaCDk5NzQwMjA1ILPTkacGMAA4ggdAC3IJNjE4NTY5MjcweACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "12_1693224875.139749", "card_id": "Q_619481780", "card_label": {"type": "new", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-a4b0b52b561281109c51e4957cb20130_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-10ef6526c602e55a8c606e46aa0cc586_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 42}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "两部门发布公告称「证券交易印花税减半」，是否预示 A 股即将进入牛市？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "财政部今日发布消息称，为活跃资本市场、提振投资者信心，自 2023 年 8 月 28 日起，证券交易印花税实施减半征收。与此同时，证监会发布阶段性收紧 IPO 及再融资节奏、限制大股东减持以及融资保证金最低比例降至 80% 等政策。 8 月 28 日，A 股开盘，指数高开，上证指数涨 5.06%，深证成指涨 5.77%，创业板指涨 6.96%。板块方面，证券概念股、房地产服务概念股、保险概念股领涨；没有板块下跌。热门个股方面，东方财富涨超 16.53%，太平洋、中信证券涨停。 对此，中国人民大学中国资本市场研究院联席院长赵锡军告诉财联社记者，继中央政治局会议提出「要活跃资本市场，提振投资者信心」后，各大部委围绕投资端、融资端、交易端出台了一系列政策，协同发力。此次证券交易印花税实施减半征收可以算是一次最为重磅的提振信心的措施。从市场影响看，历次证券交易印花税税率调整均对资本市场形成很好的提振效果，尤其是最近 2008 年内两次对于印花税的调整，市场均有非常可观的涨幅。可以说，印花税的调整是对市场的实质性利好，是可对活跃资本市场、提升投资者信心起到立竿见影效果的举措，具有鲜明的积极导向作用。 （受访者赵锡军系中国人民大学中国资本市场研究院联席院长、重阳金融研究院高级研究员，本文转自 8 月 27 日大河财立方，欢迎关注人大重阳新浪微博:@人大重阳, 微信公众号:rdcy2013）"}, "image_area": {"url": ""}, "metrics_area": {"text": "78 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/619481780"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4I+fCcl5nPzfhQEAMaCDk5OTQyNzIzIJymsKcGMAA4NEAMcgk2MTk0ODE3ODB4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "13_1693224875.141524", "card_id": "Q_619466774", "card_label": {"type": "new", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-a4b0b52b561281109c51e4957cb20130_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-10ef6526c602e55a8c606e46aa0cc586_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 53}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "老板暗示你下班走的太早了，该怎么反驳？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "公司强制要求加班到八点，并且开会暗示自己走的太早了，该怎么反驳才能让他知道无谓的加班并没有什么用？"}, "image_area": {"url": ""}, "metrics_area": {"text": "76 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/619466774"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4I+fCcl5nPzfhQEAMaCDk5OTM5Mzg3ILbpr6cGMAA4OkANcgk2MTk0NjY3NzR4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "14_1693224875.142645", "card_id": "Q_619477845", "card_label": {"type": "new", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-a4b0b52b561281109c51e4957cb20130_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-10ef6526c602e55a8c606e46aa0cc586_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 23}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "8 月 28 日，A 股开盘跳涨 5 % ，证券公司板块几乎全线涨停。如何解读 A 股这一反应？"